    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "A recipe website wants to implement a system that recommends recipes based on the user's ingredient preferences.\r\n\r\nThe <code style=\"background-color: #ececec; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">Website</code> class stores five recipes. The <code style=\"background-color: #ececec; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">Recipe</code> class stores the name of the recipe and three ingredients.\r\n\r\n✅ <strong>TO DO #1:</strong> Write the <code style=\"background-color: #ececec; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">private</code> method <code style=\"background-color: #ececec; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">resultsToString()</code> in the <code style=\"background-color: #ececec; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">Website</code> class that takes three <code style=\"background-color: #ececec; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">Recipe</code> objects as parameters and returns a <code style=\"background-color: #ececec; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">String</code> that contains each recipe’s information on separate lines.\r\n\r\n✅ <strong>TO DO #2:</strong> Write the <code style=\"background-color: #ececec; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">public</code> method <code style=\"background-color: #ececec; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">getRecommendedRecipes()</code> that takes three preferred ingredients as parameters. It should return a <code style=\"background-color: #ececec; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">String</code> of three pre-selected recipes (not filtered) using the <code style=\"background-color: #ececec; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">resultsToString()</code> method.\r\n\r\n✅ <strong>TO DO #3:</strong> In the <code style=\"background-color: #ececec; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">RecipeRunner</code> class, call the <code style=\"background-color: #ececec; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">getRecommendedRecipes()</code> method and print the result.\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: #E0D1EC; border: 1px solid #9660bf; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 1.1em; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n💡 <strong>TIP:</strong> Check out the <strong>Help & Tips</strong> tab ⬆️ for help with writing <code style=\"background-color: #ececec; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">private</code> methods.\r\n</div>\r\n",
